This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with semantic segmentation and human parsing. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it proposes an end-to-end model. Additionally, it may belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with image analysis. Finally, it may belong to the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category as it mentions the challenge of resolving deformation and multi-scale variations.
